Author: Elon Musk
Quote: “To anyone I have offended, I just want to say I reinvented electric cars and I’m sending people to Mars on a rocket ship. Did you think I was also going to be a chill, normal dude?”

Author: Mark Zuckerberg
Quote: Move fast and break things. Unless you are breaking stuff, you are not moving fast enough.

Author: Mark Zuckerberg
Quote: People don't care about what you say, they care about what you build.

Author: Temple Grandin
Quote: What would happen if the autism gene was eliminated from the gene pool? You would have a bunch of people standing around in a cave, chatting and socializing and not getting anything done.
